    <entry>
      <title>hexo建设用到的插件及命令合集</title>
      <link href="/2020/05/25/hexo%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E5%8F%8A%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86/"/>
      <url>/2020/05/25/hexo%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E5%8F%8A%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>详细流程和命令总集。</p><a id="more"></a><h1 id="Hexo-asset-image插件"><a href="#Hexo-asset-image插件" class="headerlink" title="Hexo-asset-image插件"></a>Hexo-asset-image插件</h1><p>安装</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install https://github.com/CodeFalling/hexo-asset-image --save</span><br><span class="line">当安装有cnpm时则可用(下文同理)</span><br><span class="line">cnpm install https://github.com/CodeFalling/hexo-asset-image --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>建议安装完后检查\node_modules\hexo-asset-image文件夹是否存在<br>在blog根目录下修改_config.yml文件</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">post_asset_folder: <span class="literal">false</span> 改为 <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在Git Bash Here工具于blog根目录下使用</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo n <span class="string">"blog_name"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建新文章时，在/source/_posts目录下应当出现 blog_name.md和blog_name文件夹<br>将图片放入文件夹内，然后在md中用相对路径来引用</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![anything words](blog_name/picture_name.jpg)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后先</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>看一下public/2020/5/25/index.html中的内容<br>在你插入图片的地方，显示的应该是</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=<span class="string">"/2020/05/25/blog_name/picture_name.jpg  alt="</span>anything words<span class="string">"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>当其自动修改成这样时才认为成功，如果前面没有日期或者说代码没有变化，可以认为是没有成功。</p><p>据说还有正确的引用图片方式但我没有使用就成功了，在该文章里：<br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/xjm850552586/article/details/84101345" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/xjm850552586/article/details/84101345</a></p><h1 id="Hexo-admin"><a href="#Hexo-admin" class="headerlink" title="Hexo-admin"></a>Hexo-admin</h1><p>安装</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-admin</span><br><span class="line">或</span><br><span class="line">cnpm install --save hexo-admin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改blog根目录下_config.yml(否则会出现Error: Config value “admin.deployCommand” not found或者Error: spawn hexo ENOENT之类的报错。)<br>Windows系统则在最末端加上(Mac系统看该部分末尾的参考文章)</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">admin:</span><br><span class="line">    deployCommand: `hexo-pubish.bat`</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后在同级目录新建hexo-pubish.bat文件，文件内容如下：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>启动服务器</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo server -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>即可在localhost:4000/admin/中编辑博文了<br>注：该插件也可以插入图片但这里不讲述，参考文章中有：<br><a href="https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000018488921" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000018488921</a></p><h1 id="hexo-deployer-git"><a href="#hexo-deployer-git" class="headerlink" title="hexo-deployer-git"></a>hexo-deployer-git</h1><p>hexo d后显示<br>ERROR Deployer not found: git</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-deployer-git</span><br><span class="line">或</span><br><span class="line">cnpm install --save hexo-deployer-git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>参考文章：<br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_36401046/article/details/52940313" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_36401046/article/details/52940313</a></p><h2 id="hexo常用指令-上文插件指令总集篇"><a href="#hexo常用指令-上文插件指令总集篇" class="headerlink" title="hexo常用指令+上文插件指令总集篇"></a>hexo常用指令+上文插件指令总集篇</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean //清理缓存</span><br><span class="line">hexo d  //部署</span><br><span class="line">hexo s  //在localhost:4000上运行</span><br><span class="line">hexo server -d   //在localhost:4000/admin/上运行Admin插件</span><br><span class="line">hexo n A_Blog  //新建一个名叫A_Blog的文章</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/2020/05/25/hexo%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E5%8F%8A%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86/77879578_p0.jpg" alt="孝 心 变 质"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
